      "heading": null,
      "description": "De-seed and slice up your peppers. Chop up your onion."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add a drizzle of olive oil to a pan. Add peppers and onion. Fry until soft."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add a handful of chopped coriander, a garlic clove, harissa paste and paprika. Mix well."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add your butter beans and chickpeas to the pan with their water. Simmer on a low heat for 30 minutes."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Dressing time. Mix the juice of a lemon, tahini, salt and pepper. Add water to loosen the dressing (as much as required)."
    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Add 4 generous handfuls of spinach to the pan and allow to wilt. Season with salt and pepper. Serve in a bowl with a nice drizzle of dressing on top."
